headline: CHIPOTLE MEXICAN GRILL TO ANNOUNCE FIRST QUARTER 2025 RESULTS ON APRIL 23, 2025
summary: Chipotle Mexican Grill (NYSE: CMG) will host a conference call on Wednesday, April 23, 2025 at 4:30 PM Eastern time to discuss first quarter 2025 financial results and provide a business update for the second quarter to date.
